dely by middle-class Presbyterians and Congregationalists and constituted an acceptance by elites of tempered, non-elite piety.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aRevivalszNew York (State)zJefferson CountyxHistoryy19th century. 4aHistory : American History. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / Protestant.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791487341423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791487341/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles